      <title>乌克兰部分国家未能履行防空承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/some-ukraine-are-failing-to-follow-through-on-air-defense-pledges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，乌克兰的一些北约盟友未能履行加速交付防空系统和其他军事装备以抵御俄罗斯攻势的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/some-ukraine-are-failing-to-follow-through-on-air-defense-pledges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
